16:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda avtokredit berish ko'pchilik tijorat banklari tomonidan yillik 22% dan 33% gacha stavkalarda taklif etiladi. Stavkalar kredit muddati (1-7 yil), boshlang'ich to'lov, avtomobil markasi (yangi yoki ishlatilgan) va qarz oluvchining kredit tarixiga bog'liq. Mahalliy ishlab chiqarish avtomobillari (UzAuto Motors — Chevrolet) uchun ko'pincha 19-24% stavkalar bilan maxsus dasturlar amal qiladi (alohida UzAuto dasturlari — 0% bo'lib to'lash)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Avtokredit hisoblash iste'mol kreditiga o'xshash — annuitet formulasi qo'llaniladi. Misol: 280 000 000 so'mlik Chevrolet Onix sotib olish. Boshlang'ich to'lov 30% = 84 000 000 so'm. Kredit summasi: 196 000 000 so'm 5 yilga (60 oy) yillik 20% da. Oylik to'lov ≈ 5 200 000 so'm. Umumiy to'lovlar: 312 000 000 so'm. Ortiqcha to'lov: 116 000 000 so'm (59%)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Avtokredit olish uchun kerak: pasport, daromad ma'lumotnomasi (to'lov sof daromadning 50% dan ko'p bo'lmasligi kerak), kredit tarixi. Avtokredit bo'yicha garov — sotib olinayotgan avtomobil. KASKO sug'urtasi butun kredit muddatiga majburiy, narxi avtomobil qiymatining yiliga 2-5%."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Oylik to'lovni kamaytirish uchun boshlang'ich to'lovni oshiring: 30% o'rniga 50% da oylik to'lov taxminan 30% ga kamayadi. Qisqaroq muddatga kredit olish ham foydaliroq — 5 yil o'rniga 3 yilda ortiqcha to'lov taxminan 40% ga kamayadi. Avtokreditni muddatidan oldin to'lash jarimasisz ruxsat etilgan."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Avtomobil va kredit qiymatidan tashqari qo'shimcha xarajatlarni hisobga oling: majburiy "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/osago","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"OSAGO"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" sug'urtasi (65 000 so'mdan), YHXda ro'yxatdan o'tish, GPS-treker o'rnatish, yillik transport solig'i. OSAGOni bizning OSAGO kalkulyatorimiz yordamida hisoblashingiz mumkin."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"O'zbekiston banklarida iste'mol kredit stavkalari"}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]}]]]}],"$L1e","$L1f"]}]
